{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-004__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-004", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·004.1", "text_original": "于以采蘋？南澗之濱，于以采藻？于彼行潦。", "text_normalized": "于以采蘋？南澗之濱，于以采藻？于彼行潦。", "notes": "采蘋 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-004", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·004.2", "text_original": "于以盛之？維筐及筥，于以湘之？維錡及釜。", "text_normalized": "于以盛之？維筐及筥，于以湘之？維錡及釜。", "notes": "采蘋 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-004__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-004", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·004.3", "text_original": "于以奠之？宗室牖下，誰其尸之？有齊季女。", "text_normalized": "于以奠之？宗室牖下，誰其尸之？有齊季女。", "notes": "采蘋 Chinese stanza 3."}
